wiki.summary: “Killer” is the thirteenth track off Eminem’s 2020 project "Music to Be Murdered By: Side B". Produced by the popular hip-hop producer 'd.a got that dope' who also produced some other tracks of the project, most notably “Godzilla.” On the track, Eminem raps about his fortune and success throughout his career while paying homage to multiple tracks and artists that helped him along the way. All the while Em frequently references famous serial killers for he is a true 'Killer' of the industry. Read more on Last.fm.
